track_notes: As far as Scawd Law is concerned this is a straightforward walk from a parking place by the bridge at Belshaw Pool just off the A708 Selkirk Road. The access gate to the track there was locked. Well graded tracks go as far as NT 148037.
track_title: Long round SS-142, SS-100 and SS-082

track_notes: From the parking I went to Capel Fell then Scawd Fell. There were trees down but with care they can be climbed over or under.
track_title: Circular walk Capel Fell, Scawd Fell and Croft Head
